SAfrica to Offer Parreira Coaching Job
JOHANNESBURG , November 22 ( Xinhua ) -- South African soccer authority will formally offer Brazilian Carlos Alberto Parreira the South African coaching job on Monday .
Parreira , who guided Brazil to the World Cup title in the United States four years ago , arrived in South Africa late on Friday for a five-day visit .
He will sit down with the South African Football Association on Monday to decide the details .
However , Parreira told journalists on Sunday he was also considering other offers .
South African officials apparently regard the 56-year-old as the top pick for the post while interviewing other coaches from England , Germany and the Netherlands .
